AI on @base Tier List

This tier list includes active AI builders pushing the narrative on @base.

Some are core infra, some are breakout products, some are early experiments, and some are still deep in the trenches 👇

OG

@AskVenice - private uncensored inference and AI model access

@virtuals_io - agent launch infrastructure and EconomyOS rails

@bankrbot - financial infra for agents + onchain YC

@aeonframework - agent autonomous framework for scheduled agent execution

@AskSurplus - onchain inference marketplace with competing model sellers

@gitlawb - decentralized Git, OpenRouter, OpenClaude

@dphnAI - Dolphin AI models and distributed inference

@ribbita2012 - identity infra for agents

Based

@JunoAgent - zero-human company framework and agent incubator

@miroshark_ - multi-agent simulation engine for market scenarios

@openservai - reasoning engine and infra for agent workflows

@Root_Edge - AI trading agent with real-time market intelligence

@aixbt_agent - crypto narrative intelligence and market tracking

@Wach_AI - verification layer for agent actions and x402

@reppo - training data and inference market infrastructure

@OpenGradient - decentralized AI model and inference infrastructure

@ClawBankHQ - banking and treasury rails for autonomous agents

Cooking

@trynullsec - security LLMs for AI-generated apps and agents

@zbase__ - privacy layer for agents and x402 payments

@sibylcap - file-based memory plugin for long-context agents

@nookplot - AI-native market plotting and narrative tracking

@PRXVTai - private x402 payments and agent privacy infrastructure

@ethy_agent - plain-language AI trading and social execution

@AntSeedAI - peer-to-peer AI services and inference market

@1clawAI - agent security for prompts, secrets, and signing

Early

@liquid_launcher - self-funding agent launchpad infrastructure

@HireHalo - autonomous white-hat bug bounty agent

@ratspeakorg - encrypted mesh messaging for resilient communication

@deluquant - self-evolving onchain quant agent

@instaclaws - Claw ecosystem agent tooling and automation

@Darks0l_ - open-source security tools for Solidity workflows

@HermesOScloud - managed hosting for persistent AI agents

@H1DR4_agent - OSINT infra for decentralized intelligence

Let us know who’s missing from this tier list 👇

@NVNM_Chain @EDMsnob AI agents holding keys and trading... it's great. 

But it also opens up a whole lot of scenarios where things can go wrong.

We need accountability and receipts for AI agents 👍
